snippet.title: Lily Rose – Villain (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Listen to Lily's debut single "Villain" here: https://lilyrose.ffm.to/villain.oyd

Stream/Download Lily's debut project Stronger Than I Am:
▸ https://lilyrose.lnk.to/StrongerThanIAm

Stay connected for exclusive updates:
▸ Sign Up: https://ffm.bio/lilyrose
▸ Website: https://www.lilyrosemusic.net

Get to know Lily:
TikTok: https://lilyrose.ffm.to/tiktok.oyd
Instagram:https://lilyrose.ffm.to/instagram.oyd
Facebook: https://lilyrose.ffm.to/facebook.oyd
Twitter: https://lilyrose.ffm.to/twitter.oyd

Lyrics: 

Yeah I’ve heard things, 
Goin round and round, runnin through this town, 
Like a two lane, I heard em say
I never loved you, found something new, gave up too soon, 
But that’s half the truth, one point of view

You can be the hero, I can take the fall
If thats how your story goes, then say it's all my fault
Whatever helps you sleep at night, you can make me the bad guy
Make em all believe it, If that’s how you’re feeling, I can be the villain

Didn’t have to be, 
This way you made me play the part, 
The enemy, but they’ll start to see, that ain’t me

You can be the hero, I can take the fall
If thats how your story goes, then say it's all my fault
Whatever helps you sleep at night, you can make me the bad guy
Make em all believe it, If that’s how you’re feeling, I can be the villain

What they don’t know, is I tried to make us, work it out, but I couldn’t save, yeah I couldn’t save us

You can be the hero, I can take the fall
If thats how your story goes, then say it's all my fault
Whatever helps you sleep at night, you can make me the bad guy
Make em all believe it, If that’s how you’re feeling, I can be the villain

#LilyRose
#Villain
